r-beaches.txt to order\nbh = open(path_map['kramabench-environment-hard-9/files/boston-harbor-beaches.txt']).read().splitlines()\nordered = [b for b in bh if b in qualifying]\nprint(ordered)\n\n# final print for execute_ideal\nprint('\\n'.join(ordered))", "intent": "Find beaches with all Enterococcus samples <104 between 2020-01-01 and 2024-12-31, parsing datasheet CSVs and preserving order from boston-harbor-beaches.txt", "dataset_id": "kramabench-environment-hard-9", "file_path": "files/constitution_beach_datasheet.csv"}) [toolUseId=call_Czwr8Uo8XPVZEWvvRVdT2Cfr]
